{"tid":1334821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人要學識記仇！","createTime":"2019-07-20T09:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:46:07.000Z","uid":281998,"like":72,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07014baa1c138959c2b45c8dcdaaf1ed71510eb7","tid":1334821,"uid":281998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要學識記仇！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要學識記仇！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要學識記仇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吉野家出咗聲明支持警察暴力之後，有幾多人有信心一年後都仲記得？有決心唔去食？<br />\n<br />\n為左方便大家記仇，唯有持續更新一個屬於香港人既黑名單。全力抵制藍屍商戶/食肆。<br />\n我地之後仲會嘗試將呢個黑名單地圖化。  <br />\n<strong>務求大家可以禁個制就睇到邊間唔食得、乜野唔買得。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非除咗遊行連署，其實仲有好多野可以做。<br />\n報料係連登巴絲既強項，希望大家可以幫幫手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提供資料最好包埋<br />\n商戶名： （例如吉野家、養心殿、左麟右李粥麵小菜專門店 etc）<br />\n做過咩仆街野：<br />\n供fact check既source：（新聞Link、社交媒體 Post等）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加開TG報料區：<a href=\"https://t.me/tvbloody\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbloody&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvboleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=1bf397d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbloody</a><br />\n<br />\n下一步就到全城期待既 TVB 廣告商贊助商，勢要令佢地撒回廣告。<br />\n夠料之後我地會發動全面攻擊，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">杯葛藍絲商戶，重挫TVB收入！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5b734cef9abf641168aa227baeb3d63939a7511a","tid":1334821,"uid":281998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:20:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e25a5f589b6fc4c873af875382fb78d9c526d8d","tid":1334821,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06b49f527de9992be36f77c66543f604c550d655","tid":1334821,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cf1dbd365123aa81459a67ef9bcaf3941be94fc","tid":1334821,"uid":146184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6088392acf48dcb0a61d00acdcd1788831d5486d","tid":1334821,"uid":146184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:04:48.000Z","msg":"結合埋社交媒體keep住攻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07464191c9dbf80a5019aa20a14a4ec489e9bc0","tid":1334821,"uid":5623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"求整list🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n已停食金拱門 吉野家"},{"pid":"c37186741ed17f1baedf6c1f91f14ebb9d86902a","tid":1334821,"uid":156666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHCHhyt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHCHhyt.jpg&h=ea765c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6wVj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F